flowchart LR
    R[User request] --> AUTH[Auth + tenant context]
    AUTH --> SS[Session create / lookup]
    SS --> SEARCH[search_agents]
    SEARCH --> BUILD[build_deep_agent]
    BUILD --> LLM1[Supervisor LLM call]
    LLM1 -->|tool_call| TOOL[Tool / subagent]
    TOOL --> LLM2[Subagent LLM call]
    LLM2 --> LLM1
    LLM1 --> FU[Followups]
    FU --> PERSIST[add_messages]
    PERSIST --> CLIENT[SSE close]
